Function Reference/the author posts « WordPress Codex
-----------

Displays the total number of posts an author has published. Drafts and
private posts aren't counted. This tag must be used within [The
Loop](/The_Loop "The Loop").

Usage
-----

`  <?php the_author_posts(); ?> `

Example
-------

Displays the author's name and number of posts.

    <p><?php the_author(); ?> has blogged <?php the_author_posts(); ?> 
    posts</p>

Harriett Smith has blogged 425 posts.

\

Parameters
----------

This tag does not accept any parameters.

